<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Elsen
                                <expan>Olslegerin<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu Wertheim, und <add>Dorothea</add>,
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> tohter, und auch Ulrich Tumirnihts,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, wegen etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Tumirniht und auch
                            <expan>Seicze<ex>n</ex></expan> Tumirniht,
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> vater, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und czu rede gesaczt in gegenwertikeit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> poten. Die
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz
                        sie der <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<add>Elsen</add> noch <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>toht<ex>er</ex></expan></add> von dheins gedings wegen nihts
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; deuht sie aber, daz sie
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czu in icht <expan>zu
                                sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> sie ir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> irem
                                <expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
